g.text: Theheliocentricmodel,inwhichtheearthgoes around the sun, was first proposed by Copernicus and was debated for some time because there was no way to test it. Experiments are needed to test new theories and ideas.
Adapted from: Fraknoi, A., Morrison, D., & Wolff, S. C. (2018). Astronomy. OpenStax. https://openstax.org/details/books/astronomy
